### 4. **Performance Display Label** (`lblPerformanceMetrics`)

A visual component on the right side of the form that displays real-time performance metrics.

**Location**: Right edge of form, positioned below the toggle panel
**Contents**: 
- Algorithm name and current mode (SLOW or FAST)
- Last execution time, CPU %, and memory allocation
- Slow vs Fast comparison (if both modes have been executed)
- Double-click hint for text copying

**Automatic Updates**: Display refreshes immediately after each algorithm execution via `UpdatePerformanceDisplay()`

